/The-Charlatans.-Credit-PRESS-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-Charlatans.-Credit-PRESS-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-Charlatans.-Credit-PRESS-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/The-Charlatans">The Charlatans</a>宣布重新发行《Up To Our Hips》的扩展版，以庆祝该专辑诞生 30 周年。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/tim-burgess-soundtrack-of-my-life-3750733">我的生活原声带：蒂姆·伯吉斯</a></strong></li></ul><p>乐队第三张专辑的新扩展版将以多种格式提供，包括 2XLP、CD 和数字版本，并将包含原始专辑以及 10 首额外曲目，全部由乐队主唱<a href="/artists/Tim-Burgess">Tim Burgess</a>策划。额外曲目还包括为 Steve Lamacq 和 Jo Whiley Show 录制的两首 BBC 现场会议歌曲，以及 B 面、交替混音和剪辑。</p><p> 《Up To Our Hips》30 周年纪念再版还将配备特殊包装，其中包含 Nik Void 重新设计的全新艺术品。 LP 将压在汽油蓝色生物乙烯基上。再版定于 11 月 8 日通过 Beggars Arkive 发行，可<a href="https://thecharlatans.ffm.to/uptoourhips30th" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>预订。 </p><figure id="attachment_3797096" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3797096" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3797096" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-Charlatans-Up-To-Our-Hips-30th-anniversary-reissue.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" alt="骗子乐队《Up To Our Hips》30 周年纪念版再版。图片来源：新闻界" width="2000" height="2000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-Charlatans-Up-To-Our-Hips-30th-anniversary-reissue.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-Charlatans-Up-To-Our-Hips-30th-anniversary-reissue.-Credit-PRESS-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-Charlatans-Up-To-Our-Hips-30th-anniversary-reissue.-Credit-PRESS-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-Charlatans-Up-To-Our-Hips-30th-anniversary-reissue.-Credit-PRESS-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-Charlatans-Up-To-Our-Hips-30th-anniversary-reissue.-Cred